\par }\pard \qj\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\f5\cgrid0 \page 
\par }{\cs16\super #{\footnote \pard\plain \sl240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\lang1040\cgrid {\cs16\super #}{\f16\fs24\cgrid0 CalcoliMedia}}${\footnote \pard\plain \sl240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\lang1040\cgrid {
