\cs16\super $}{\f16\fs24\cgrid0 Calcoli: Rapporto}}K{\footnote \pard\plain \sl240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\lang1040\cgrid {\cs16\super K}{\f16\fs24\cgrid0 Calcoli, rapporto}}}{\b\f5\fs24\cgrid0 Calcoli: Rapporto
